7) Reporting & Remediation Templates (what to include тАФ quick checklist) ЁЯУЭ

Finding title, location (physical), severity, business impact, non-sensitive evidence (logs, OTDR anomaly), remediation steps, owner, timeline, compliance notes. Use NIST SP 800-115 guidance for test documentation and handling evidence. 



